* Add python snippet to limit build to softfp on arm, e.g.:
python __anonymous() {
    tunes = bb.data.getVar("TUNE_FEATURES", d, 1)
    if not tunes:
        return
    pkgn = bb.data.getVar("PN", d, 1)
    pkgv = bb.data.getVar("PV", d, 1)
    if "callconvention-hard" in tunes:
        bb.warn("%s-%s ONLY supports softfp mode for now" % (pkgn, pkgv))
        raise bb.parse.SkipPackage("%s-%s ONLY supports softfp mode for now" % (pkgn, pkgv))
}

